    """
    Party in a security lending arrangement who can demand closure
    (temrination) of the agreement.

    :cvar BORROWER: Initial borrower to the SBL transaction.
    :cvar LENDER: Initial lender to SBL transaction.
    :cvar EITHER: Either Lender or Borrower to the SBL transaction.
    :cvar AS_DEFINED_IN_MASTER_AGREEMENT: As defined in Master
        Agreement.
    """

